<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Share Your Wedding Experience</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table role="presentation" width="600px" style="background: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    <!-- Logo hoặc Tên Host -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="text-align: center; padding: 15px;">
                            <a href="{host}" style="text-decoration: none;">
                            </a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="text-align: center;">
                            <h2 style="color: #333;">Share Your Wedding Experience</h2>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 20px; font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
                            <p>Hi <strong>{recipientName}</strong>,</p>

                            <p>It was a pleasure to be a part of your wedding! 🎉</p>

                            <p>If you have a few moments, can you share your experience with other engaged couples on 
                               <a href="https://www.hitched.co.uk" style="color: #0073e6; text-decoration: none;">hitched.co.uk</a>? 
                               Your review of our services will help them plan their wedding.</p>

                            <p>Thanks,</p>
                            <p style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">Best,</p>
                            <p style="color: #0073e6; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;">{senderName}</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Nút đánh giá -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="text-align: center; padding: 10px;">
                            <a href="https://www.hitched.co.uk" 
                               style="background-color: #0073e6; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; 
                                      text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px;">
                                Leave a Review
                            </a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Phần Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #888; padding-top: 20px;">
                            <p>If you did not request this email, please ignore it.</p>
                            <p>Sent from <a href="{HostUrl}" style="color: #0073e6; text-decoration: none;">{hostName}</a></p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
